1
00:00:14,480 --> 00:00:16,199
(After being a substitute for so long,)

2
00:00:17,440 --> 00:00:18,480
(will I forget)

3
00:00:20,600 --> 00:00:21,719
(who I truly am?)

4
00:00:36,520 --> 00:00:38,000
(They call me He Rufei.)

5
00:00:38,359 --> 00:00:38,920
Kneel.

6
00:00:39,719 --> 00:00:41,240
(The eldest son of the He family.)

7
00:00:42,640 --> 00:00:43,759
(Since childhood,)

8
00:00:44,840 --> 00:00:46,000
(I was disguised as a boy.)

9
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:47,039
(Visionary Foresight)

10
00:00:47,039 --> 00:00:48,640
(I've always had to wear a mask.)

11
00:00:49,520 --> 00:00:50,359
(They said,)

12
00:00:51,520 --> 00:00:52,079
("live")

13
00:00:52,960 --> 00:00:54,176
("without recognition")

14
00:00:55,280 --> 00:00:55,840
("and die")

15
00:00:57,039 --> 00:00:58,640
("without a trace.")

16
00:01:03,280 --> 00:01:03,840
(I hated it.)

17
00:01:03,840 --> 00:01:04,400
Remember.

18
00:01:05,439 --> 00:01:06,560
(Yet found solace too.)

19
00:01:08,200 --> 00:01:09,599
(This cold mask)

20
00:01:10,319 --> 00:01:11,280
(smothered my identity)

21
00:01:12,560 --> 00:01:13,959
(yet forged my purpose.)

22
00:01:18,079 --> 00:01:19,120
(Amidst the smoke of war)

23
00:01:19,760 --> 00:01:20,840
(and seas of blood,)

24
00:01:21,879 --> 00:01:23,000
(I forgot life and death)

25
00:01:23,920 --> 00:01:25,040
(and stopped wondering)

26
00:01:25,640 --> 00:01:26,799
(who I am)

27
00:01:27,519 --> 00:01:28,640
(beneath the mask.)

28
00:01:31,719 --> 00:01:33,519
(From a nameless foot soldier,)

29
00:01:34,879 --> 00:01:35,519
(I fought)

30
00:01:35,519 --> 00:01:37,439
(to become
the invincible General Feihong.)

31
00:01:42,159 --> 00:01:43,200
(But in the end,)

32
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:45,319
(who is General Feihong?)

33
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:47,000
(Who)

34
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:49,719
(am I?)

35
00:02:07,891 --> 00:02:10,695
♪Shrugging off past burdens♪

36
00:02:10,695 --> 00:02:13,284
♪Beneath the mask, who am I?♪

37
00:02:13,951 --> 00:02:17,359
♪Release and find wider shores♪

38
00:02:19,056 --> 00:02:22,063
♪Love's a riddle, and rain pours heavy♪

39
00:02:22,438 --> 00:02:24,962
♪Crossed paths, now downward fall♪

40
00:02:25,306 --> 00:02:28,741
♪From dust arises starlight's spark♪

41
00:02:30,495 --> 00:02:35,715
♪Tearing through
the night's dense blockade♪

42
00:02:36,397 --> 00:02:41,479
♪Heart's flame illuminates all solitude♪

43
00:02:42,271 --> 00:02:44,767
♪Let time's sails drift endlessly♪

44
00:02:44,767 --> 00:02:47,375
♪Through wandering exile♪

45
00:02:47,891 --> 00:02:55,156
♪Breaking free from the cocoon,
I start anew♪

46
00:02:56,127 --> 00:02:58,883
♪Moon as song, life as flame♪

47
00:02:58,943 --> 00:03:01,783
♪Nameless heart clings fiercely♪

48
00:03:02,076 --> 00:03:03,103
♪Let me♪

49
00:03:03,295 --> 00:03:07,378
♪Charge toward the next raging river♪

50
00:03:07,828 --> 00:03:10,507
♪Moon darts, snow falls♪

51
00:03:10,791 --> 00:03:13,492
♪We tread rugged paths to reunite♪

52
00:03:13,663 --> 00:03:15,133
♪Hands held tight♪

53
00:03:15,133 --> 00:03:19,309
♪We forever live for love's sake♪

54
00:03:19,660 --> 00:03:29,919
♪Shadow's spear burns fiercely♪

55
00:03:31,346 --> 00:03:37,056
=Legend of The Female General=

56
00:03:47,056 --> 00:03:50,192
=Episode 1=

57
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:52,719
(In the 20th year
of Wei's Qingyuan era,)

58
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:54,639
(Battlefield of Mingshui)
(Wutuo invaded Wei again.)

59
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:56,919
(Emperor Chengping)

60
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:58,759
(ordered General Xiao Zhongwu,)

61
00:03:58,759 --> 00:03:59,759
(Xiao Army's commander)

62
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:01,520
(who beat Wutuo five years ago,)

63
00:04:02,039 --> 00:04:03,120
(Xiao Zhongwu, Xiao Army's Commander)
(to march to battle.)

64
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:05,759
(But at Mingshui's final battle,)

65
00:04:06,639 --> 00:04:08,039
(30,000 Xiao troops)

66
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:09,919
(fell into an ambush.)

67
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:14,479
Xiao Zhongwu,

68
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:15,960
He Rufei's Fuyue Army

69
00:04:16,240 --> 00:04:17,080
won't be coming.

70
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:18,599
Surrender,

71
00:04:18,960 --> 00:04:20,280
and we'll spare you.

72
00:04:20,599 --> 00:04:21,759
He Rufei

73
00:04:23,599 --> 00:04:25,080
will come without fail!

74
00:04:25,599 --> 00:04:28,160
Wei soldiers

75
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:34,839
choose death over surrender.

76
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:38,000
Charge!

77
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:59,040
General Xiao!

78
00:05:00,879 --> 00:05:01,680
General Xiao!

79
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:08,959
General Xiao!

80
00:05:15,439 --> 00:05:15,959
Father!

81
00:05:24,548 --> 00:05:26,839
(Xiao Jue, styled Huaijin,
General Fengyun)

82
00:05:26,839 --> 00:05:27,879
He Rufei,

83
00:05:28,176 --> 00:05:29,279
(General Feihong of Wei)

84
00:05:29,279 --> 00:05:31,240
Huayuan is less than a hundred li
from Mingshui.

85
00:05:32,120 --> 00:05:33,879
Why has your reinforcement
arrived so late?

86
00:05:44,680 --> 00:05:45,639
A rope saws wood.

87
00:05:45,879 --> 00:05:46,959
Water penetrates stones.

88
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:48,639
One day,

89
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:50,279
you two will become

90
00:05:50,279 --> 00:05:51,120
Wei's Twin Stars.

91
00:05:51,839 --> 00:05:52,720
With joint forces,

92
00:05:53,279 --> 00:05:55,120
you shall wield the swords
to guard our land

93
00:05:55,639 --> 00:05:56,480
and its people.

94
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:10,800
You are unworthy

95
00:06:10,839 --> 00:06:13,000
of the Qinglang Sword
my father entrusted to you.

96
00:06:24,879 --> 00:06:26,480
(Yaojing City)
General Feihong's returned triumphantly!

97
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:27,759
General Feihong!

98
00:06:28,639 --> 00:06:30,279
Welcome, General Feihong!

99
00:06:30,352 --> 00:06:40,304
(General Feihong's Mansion)

100
00:07:05,879 --> 00:07:06,480
Young Master,

101
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:08,240
the Master awaits you in his study.

102
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:20,560
Ermao.

103
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:25,000
Madam,

104
00:07:25,519 --> 00:07:26,360
now that you're here,

105
00:07:26,439 --> 00:07:27,560
visit the Young Lady.

106
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:29,519
Watch your tongue.

107
00:07:30,519 --> 00:07:31,759
There is only the Young Master.

108
00:07:32,600 --> 00:07:33,360
The Young Lady...

109
00:07:34,990 --> 00:07:35,984
(Tang Jia, He Yan's mother)

110
00:07:37,959 --> 00:07:39,439
She's recuperating at Yuhua Temple.

111
00:07:56,279 --> 00:07:56,816
Sit.

112
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:02,720
Yan,

113
00:08:03,439 --> 00:08:04,519
you've been away for years,

114
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:07,519
(He Yuansheng, He Yan's father)
enduring military hardships.

115
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:09,839
It must have been hard.

116
00:08:10,879 --> 00:08:11,480
Father,

117
00:08:11,879 --> 00:08:12,759
it's not hard at all.

118
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:14,519
Honoring our family

119
00:08:14,839 --> 00:08:15,720
fills me with joy.

120
00:08:16,759 --> 00:08:17,328
Yan,

121
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:20,000
I'm glad you're home.

122
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:21,519
For a young lady,

123
00:08:21,560 --> 00:08:22,600
to wield weapons

124
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:23,920
is improper.

125
00:08:24,319 --> 00:08:25,199
Honoring the family

126
00:08:25,399 --> 00:08:27,040
should be men's duty.

127
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:29,800
Now that you're back,

128
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:31,800
it's time to embrace your true identity

129
00:08:31,839 --> 00:08:32,720
as a woman.

130
00:08:33,120 --> 00:08:34,120
About our family's title,

131
00:08:34,399 --> 00:08:35,439
you don't need to worry.

132
00:08:35,759 --> 00:08:37,360
I have a solution.

133
00:08:38,879 --> 00:08:39,519
A solution?

134
00:08:40,519 --> 00:08:41,279
What solution?

135
00:08:41,680 --> 00:08:42,399
You've sacrificed

136
00:08:42,399 --> 00:08:43,559
for our family for years.

137
00:08:43,919 --> 00:08:44,919
It's been tough for you.

138
00:08:47,759 --> 00:08:48,799
From now on,

139
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:50,519
let me handle these matters.

140
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:55,200
This is

141
00:08:55,320 --> 00:08:56,799
your brother you never met,

142
00:08:56,919 --> 00:08:57,559
(He Rufei, He Yan's elder brother)
He Rufei.

143
00:08:58,320 --> 00:08:58,960
When you came

144
00:08:58,960 --> 00:09:00,360
with your mother at three,

145
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:01,639
due to his congenital frailty,

146
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:03,919
he had been recuperating
at Yuhua Temple.

147
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:06,360
That's why you had to replace him.

148
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:07,799
Now

149
00:09:07,919 --> 00:09:09,320
your brother has fully recovered

150
00:09:09,519 --> 00:09:10,200
and returned.

151
00:09:10,879 --> 00:09:11,960
Both of you

152
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:13,720
should return to your proper places.

153
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:14,960
Our family's act

154
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:16,600
of replacing a son

155
00:09:16,759 --> 00:09:17,440
with a daughter

156
00:09:17,480 --> 00:09:19,360
can then be quietly erased.

157
00:09:23,399 --> 00:09:24,000
Father,

158
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:27,519
is this your solution?

159
00:09:31,519 --> 00:09:32,080
Yan,

160
00:09:32,559 --> 00:09:34,159
you must consider
our family's interests.

161
00:09:34,519 --> 00:09:35,279
Our family

162
00:09:35,679 --> 00:09:37,519
is a pillar of Confucian academia

163
00:09:37,799 --> 00:09:38,799
and a leader in literary.

164
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:41,840
Now, abandoning culture
for martial pursuits,

165
00:09:42,360 --> 00:09:42,919
- we...
- Father.

166
00:09:43,919 --> 00:09:45,559
It was precisely to not disappoint you

167
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:46,720
and to guard

168
00:09:46,720 --> 00:09:47,759
our family's honor

169
00:09:48,720 --> 00:09:50,320
that I strove to achieve military glory.

170
00:09:50,879 --> 00:09:51,720
I hoped that one day

171
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:54,080
I'd become a hero
like General Xiao Zhongwu.

172
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:56,879
You wished to emulate Xiao Zhongwu?

173
00:09:58,080 --> 00:10:00,000
Xiao Zhongwu was a traitor to Wei.

174
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:02,399
It was all due to his reckless ambition

175
00:10:02,679 --> 00:10:03,799
and warmongering.

176
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:05,799
Soldiers wield swords

177
00:10:06,519 --> 00:10:07,320
to guard the land

178
00:10:08,159 --> 00:10:09,000
and its people.

179
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:11,440
General Xiao taught me those words.

180
00:10:12,519 --> 00:10:13,320
I refuse to believe

181
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:15,720
he was a warmonger.

182
00:10:16,759 --> 00:10:17,840
Tomorrow, I'll attend court

183
00:10:18,480 --> 00:10:20,240
and demand justice for General Xiao.

184
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:22,720
Even at the cost of my military honors,

185
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:24,279
I won't hesitate.

186
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:33,399
(Wei's Imperial Palace)
(In Mingshui Battle,)

187
00:10:33,919 --> 00:10:37,240
(Wei lost over 30,000 soldiers.)

188
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:40,559
Commander Xiao Zhongwu
bears full responsibility.

189
00:10:40,919 --> 00:10:44,360
(Emperor Chengping of Wei)
The Xiaos shall bury him as a commoner

190
00:10:44,879 --> 00:10:47,600
and be stripped of military command

191
00:10:48,120 --> 00:10:50,399
as punishment.

192
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:53,072
Your Majesty,

193
00:10:54,039 --> 00:10:54,879
my father

194
00:10:55,519 --> 00:10:57,320
was no warmonger.

195
00:10:58,080 --> 00:10:58,799
Our army had

196
00:10:58,840 --> 00:10:59,960
ambushes set

197
00:10:59,960 --> 00:11:00,840
throughout Mingshui.

198
00:11:01,840 --> 00:11:03,120
Yet on the day of battle,

199
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:04,840
the Wutuo people

200
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:07,720
somehow destroyed
all ambush points beforehand.

201
00:11:08,399 --> 00:11:10,120
There must have been
a leak of intelligence.

202
00:11:10,679 --> 00:11:12,879
I implore Your Majesty
to reopen this case

203
00:11:13,679 --> 00:11:14,919
to clear my father's name

204
00:11:15,639 --> 00:11:17,200
and restore justice

205
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:19,720
for Xiao Army soldiers.

206
00:11:20,679 --> 00:11:22,240
By imperial decree,

207
00:11:22,559 --> 00:11:27,080
summon General Feihong, He Rufei.

208
00:11:50,320 --> 00:11:53,879
I, He Rufei,
pay respects to Your Majesty.

209
00:11:56,360 --> 00:11:56,879
Rise.

210
00:11:58,519 --> 00:11:59,200
Thank you.

211
00:12:01,480 --> 00:12:02,080
General He,

212
00:12:02,519 --> 00:12:03,360
in Mingshui Battle,

213
00:12:03,639 --> 00:12:04,759
was there more

214
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:05,919
to Xiao Army's defeat?

215
00:12:06,759 --> 00:12:07,639
Your Majesty,

216
00:12:08,279 --> 00:12:09,320
there was no more story

217
00:12:10,320 --> 00:12:11,480
to Mingshui Battle.

218
00:12:12,600 --> 00:12:13,879
If not for General Xiao's

219
00:12:13,879 --> 00:12:15,120
reckless pursuit of glory

220
00:12:15,639 --> 00:12:17,200
and direct confrontation with Wutuo,

221
00:12:17,480 --> 00:12:18,559
coupled with his refusal

222
00:12:18,559 --> 00:12:20,320
to request aid from our Fuyue Army,

223
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:22,879
how could the battle
have turned so tragic?

224
00:12:25,159 --> 00:12:26,799
He Rufei!

225
00:12:27,919 --> 00:12:28,879
General Fengyun,

226
00:12:29,159 --> 00:12:30,559
I tried to reason with you.

227
00:12:30,759 --> 00:12:32,679
Yet, to absolve your father's sins,

228
00:12:32,879 --> 00:12:34,000
you twisted the truth

229
00:12:34,039 --> 00:12:35,440
and made baseless accusations.

230
00:12:35,919 --> 00:12:37,480
I mobilized troops immediately

231
00:12:37,679 --> 00:12:39,159
upon receiving the distress message

232
00:12:39,279 --> 00:12:40,720
without a moment's hesitation.

233
00:12:40,759 --> 00:12:42,279
He Rufei,

234
00:12:44,320 --> 00:12:45,720
after all these years apart,

235
00:12:48,600 --> 00:12:50,559
why did you become so wretched?

236
00:13:06,799 --> 00:13:07,720
You dare attempt

237
00:13:07,720 --> 00:13:09,320
to plead for a sinner?

238
00:13:09,639 --> 00:13:10,159
You're

239
00:13:10,360 --> 00:13:12,080
dragging our entire family to graves.

240
00:13:12,080 --> 00:13:13,120
- Father.
- (I've meticulously imitated)

241
00:13:13,279 --> 00:13:15,879
(your handwriting
and behavioral patterns.)

242
00:13:15,960 --> 00:13:16,600
(Imitating?)

243
00:13:16,679 --> 00:13:19,840
(Since you're unwilling to swap identities,
we'll talk about it later.)

244
00:13:19,879 --> 00:13:21,679
(You've sacrificed
a lot for your brother.)

245
00:13:21,879 --> 00:13:22,600
(It's been tough.)

246
00:13:23,320 --> 00:13:26,399
(Let your brother express
his gratitude to you)

247
00:13:26,840 --> 00:13:27,960
(and have this cup of tea.)

248
00:13:43,360 --> 00:13:46,320
General Fengyun
breached court etiquette.

249
00:13:46,879 --> 00:13:50,799
But His Majesty acknowledges
the Xiao family's military merits.

250
00:13:51,159 --> 00:13:52,840
As a warning, he shall be punished

251
00:13:53,159 --> 00:13:54,399
with 20 strokes

252
00:13:55,240 --> 00:13:58,080
and kneel outside the hall till dawn

253
00:13:58,440 --> 00:14:00,799
to reflect on his transgressions.

254
00:14:16,771 --> 00:14:19,376
(Memorial Tablet of Mother, Song Wan;
Memorial Tablet of Father, Xiao Zhongwu)

255
00:14:29,412 --> 00:14:30,896
(People's Guardian of Loyalty and Valor)

256
00:14:46,115 --> 00:14:47,482
(People's Guardian of Loyalty and Valor)

257
00:14:51,759 --> 00:14:53,519
Punishment carried out.

258
00:15:10,960 --> 00:15:11,600
Your Majesty,

259
00:15:12,440 --> 00:15:13,600
I admit fault.

260
00:15:14,639 --> 00:15:16,679
I request to lead troops to Que City

261
00:15:17,480 --> 00:15:18,679
to reclaim our lost territory

262
00:15:19,720 --> 00:15:21,000
and atone for my sins.

263
00:15:32,960 --> 00:15:33,559
Your Majesty,

264
00:15:33,759 --> 00:15:35,759
I'll sign a military pledge.

265
00:15:37,600 --> 00:15:38,879
If Que City isn't reclaimed,

266
00:15:39,240 --> 00:15:40,279
I vow never to return.

267
00:15:57,559 --> 00:15:58,879
General Fengyun,

268
00:15:59,240 --> 00:16:02,480
(Xu Jingfu, Prime Minister of Wei)
His Majesty has granted your request.

269
00:16:05,799 --> 00:16:07,320
Gratitude to Your Majesty.

270
00:16:09,600 --> 00:16:11,440
However, Wei's soldiers

271
00:16:11,600 --> 00:16:14,480
shall not be sent to futile deaths.

272
00:16:15,639 --> 00:16:16,600
Xiao Jue,

273
00:16:17,039 --> 00:16:20,240
the court won't provide any troops.

274
00:16:20,600 --> 00:16:22,519
Recover the territory

275
00:16:23,240 --> 00:16:25,200
through your own means.

276
00:16:29,720 --> 00:16:30,399
I

277
00:16:30,919 --> 00:16:31,639
accept the decree.

278
00:16:33,960 --> 00:16:34,840
Thanks, Your Majesty.

279
00:16:54,840 --> 00:16:56,879
(Even if at the cost of all,)

280
00:16:57,759 --> 00:17:01,519
(I will clear my father's name.)

281
00:17:05,956 --> 00:17:10,608
(Several days later)

282
00:17:15,651 --> 00:17:20,048
(Yuhua Temple)

283
00:17:29,079 --> 00:17:29,759
Miss.

284
00:17:32,839 --> 00:17:33,519
Miss.

285
00:17:34,000 --> 00:17:35,480
Take a walk with me by the roses.

286
00:17:36,119 --> 00:17:36,784
Okay.

287
00:17:40,559 --> 00:17:41,319
Be careful.

288
00:17:45,920 --> 00:17:47,359
There are steps ahead.

289
00:17:53,359 --> 00:17:55,599
(59, 60,)

290
00:17:56,680 --> 00:17:57,400
(61...)

291
00:18:00,079 --> 00:18:01,240
You're so straightforward,

292
00:18:01,720 --> 00:18:03,599
unlike the delicate noble ladies

293
00:18:03,720 --> 00:18:04,519
visiting the temple.

294
00:18:08,599 --> 00:18:09,160
Yixin,

295
00:18:10,759 --> 00:18:11,440
if I turn right

296
00:18:12,279 --> 00:18:13,000
and go forward,

297
00:18:13,440 --> 00:18:13,960
will it lead

298
00:18:14,039 --> 00:18:15,160
to the rear courtyard wall?

299
00:18:16,319 --> 00:18:17,680
Yes, it'll be the rear wall.

300
00:18:17,960 --> 00:18:20,119
Beyond lies the hidden path I use

301
00:18:20,119 --> 00:18:21,000
to leave here.

302
00:18:21,680 --> 00:18:22,680
Past the canyon crevice,

303
00:18:22,880 --> 00:18:24,319
it'll be beyond Yuhua Temple.

304
00:18:26,240 --> 00:18:27,240
Show me around.

305
00:18:28,119 --> 00:18:28,816
Okay.

306
00:18:35,684 --> 00:18:38,256
(Ding Yi, He Rufei's guard)

307
00:18:39,720 --> 00:18:41,319
Father showed mercy and spared her life

308
00:18:42,160 --> 00:18:43,519
due to family ties.

309
00:18:44,319 --> 00:18:46,160
But even blinded by poison,

310
00:18:46,720 --> 00:18:48,519
she remains a threat.

311
00:18:49,480 --> 00:18:51,119
I'll send her to Yuhua Temple first.

312
00:18:51,680 --> 00:18:52,680
Watch her closely.

313
00:18:53,799 --> 00:18:54,960
Spread that word

314
00:18:55,240 --> 00:18:57,599
that Miss He's condition
has suddenly worsened.

315
00:18:59,640 --> 00:19:00,799
Then...

316
00:19:03,440 --> 00:19:05,000
I will handle it impeccably.

317
00:19:14,039 --> 00:19:15,359
(From meditation room to bridge,)

318
00:19:15,720 --> 00:19:16,680
(it takes 61 steps.)

319
00:19:20,599 --> 00:19:21,720
(After the bridge)

320
00:19:22,279 --> 00:19:23,200
(and seven more steps,)

321
00:19:23,920 --> 00:19:25,319
(I'll reach the roses by the pond.)

322
00:19:26,119 --> 00:19:27,720
(Then bypass the roses and turn right.)

323
00:19:35,119 --> 00:19:37,000
(Did I miscalculate my stride today?)

324
00:19:38,640 --> 00:19:39,680
(Or did I miscount?)

325
00:20:17,240 --> 00:20:17,759
Who are you?

326
00:20:19,960 --> 00:20:20,640
Forgive me, miss.

327
00:20:20,920 --> 00:20:21,480
I am merely

328
00:20:22,279 --> 00:20:23,720
a devotee visiting this temple.

329
00:20:24,160 --> 00:20:24,759
No offense.

330
00:20:25,880 --> 00:20:28,240
Yuhua Temple's back courtyard
lies in the northwest corner.

331
00:20:29,240 --> 00:20:30,319
Devotees' meditation rooms

332
00:20:31,039 --> 00:20:32,079
are in the eastern part.

333
00:20:34,839 --> 00:20:35,599
It seems you think

334
00:20:35,960 --> 00:20:37,279
that I harbor ill intentions.

335
00:20:38,359 --> 00:20:39,799
If you truly wish to die,

336
00:20:40,559 --> 00:20:42,400
why care about my potential harm?

337
00:20:43,759 --> 00:20:45,160
(Wishing to die?)

338
00:20:45,839 --> 00:20:46,759
Our parents gave us

339
00:20:47,240 --> 00:20:48,000
our physical forms.

340
00:20:49,799 --> 00:20:51,519
One more step and you'd enter the pond.

341
00:20:52,079 --> 00:20:54,079
If you disrespect life so casually

342
00:20:55,039 --> 00:20:56,799
and disregard
your parents' nurturing grace,

343
00:20:57,920 --> 00:20:59,319
then proceed as you will.

344
00:21:00,000 --> 00:21:01,119
I won't stop you.

345
00:21:03,920 --> 00:21:05,000
Nurturing grace?

346
00:21:06,160 --> 00:21:07,559
They denied me even the chance

347
00:21:07,599 --> 00:21:08,319
to speak.

348
00:21:09,039 --> 00:21:10,680
They blinded me and abandoned me here.

349
00:21:12,160 --> 00:21:13,119
In that case,

350
00:21:14,759 --> 00:21:15,480
my life

351
00:21:16,200 --> 00:21:17,359
is now mine to command.

352
00:21:18,720 --> 00:21:19,720
In desperation,

353
00:21:21,400 --> 00:21:21,960
death

354
00:21:23,480 --> 00:21:24,640
becomes easier than living.

355
00:21:25,960 --> 00:21:26,839
If you're truly tough,

356
00:21:26,920 --> 00:21:27,880
blindness matters not.

357
00:21:29,440 --> 00:21:30,200
Even blind,

358
00:21:31,000 --> 00:21:31,920
aim to be

359
00:21:33,119 --> 00:21:34,119
the most special of all.

360
00:21:39,000 --> 00:21:39,759
Give me your hand.

361
00:21:47,960 --> 00:21:49,200
This osmanthus candy

362
00:21:50,480 --> 00:21:53,039
is the last piece left in the world.

363
00:21:55,920 --> 00:21:57,039
Though inedible now,

364
00:21:58,079 --> 00:21:59,039
it remains sweet.

365
00:22:03,160 --> 00:22:03,880
I won't know

366
00:22:04,240 --> 00:22:05,000
until I taste it.

367
00:22:07,519 --> 00:22:09,599
Though bitter at first taste,

368
00:22:09,960 --> 00:22:11,880
its core holds enduring sweetness.

369
00:22:16,400 --> 00:22:17,400
Is the moon tonight

370
00:22:19,480 --> 00:22:20,200
beautiful?

371
00:22:33,480 --> 00:22:34,640
Bright moon like frost.

372
00:22:36,640 --> 00:22:37,720
Gentle breeze like water.

373
00:22:40,119 --> 00:22:41,559
The serene beauty is endless.

374
00:22:56,799 --> 00:22:57,960
I moved the roses

375
00:22:58,400 --> 00:23:00,720
to stage an accidental drowning

376
00:23:01,160 --> 00:23:02,480
for Young Lady at Yuhua Temple.

377
00:23:03,119 --> 00:23:03,880
But Young Lady

378
00:23:04,279 --> 00:23:05,359
was pulled back by Xiao Jue

379
00:23:06,519 --> 00:23:07,559
and avoided falling.

380
00:23:07,920 --> 00:23:08,839
Why would Xiao Jue

381
00:23:08,839 --> 00:23:09,759
appear there?

382
00:23:11,279 --> 00:23:12,519
No matter who intervenes,

383
00:23:12,920 --> 00:23:14,359
that woman cannot be saved.

384
00:23:20,039 --> 00:23:21,480
Let her escape then

385
00:23:22,440 --> 00:23:23,640
and die

386
00:23:23,960 --> 00:23:25,720
on her way to appeal to the emperor.

387
00:23:39,519 --> 00:23:41,519
(Beyond lies the hidden path I use)

388
00:23:41,519 --> 00:23:42,440
(to leave here.)

389
00:23:43,240 --> 00:23:45,680
(Past the canyon crevice,
it'll be beyond Yuhua Temple.)

390
00:24:18,119 --> 00:24:21,559
Young Lady, let me send you
on your final journey.

391
00:24:22,640 --> 00:24:25,160
In your next life,
avoid being born a He.

392
00:25:10,720 --> 00:25:12,400
Your continued existence
remains a threat

393
00:25:12,400 --> 00:25:13,359
to the He family.

394
00:25:14,200 --> 00:25:15,119
A mere woman

395
00:25:15,480 --> 00:25:16,960
daring to seek military glory?

396
00:25:17,599 --> 00:25:19,119
Preposterous delusions!

397
00:26:00,323 --> 00:26:04,304
(One month later)

398
00:26:39,319 --> 00:26:40,319
(I can see again.)

399
00:26:54,160 --> 00:26:55,000
(Where am I?)

400
00:26:56,160 --> 00:26:57,279
(Didn't I die?)

401
00:27:14,599 --> 00:27:16,000
With great effort,

402
00:27:16,000 --> 00:27:16,559
I saved you

403
00:27:16,920 --> 00:27:18,000
and restored your vision.

404
00:27:18,240 --> 00:27:19,079
Why do you

405
00:27:19,119 --> 00:27:19,799
keep moving?

406
00:27:20,920 --> 00:27:21,680
Master.

407
00:27:22,083 --> 00:27:24,080
(Liu Buwang, He Yan's master)

408
00:27:26,359 --> 00:27:27,880
Last I saw you so weakened

409
00:27:28,519 --> 00:27:29,640
was when I rescued you

410
00:27:30,200 --> 00:27:31,680
from that mountain of corpses

411
00:27:32,039 --> 00:27:33,160
on the battlefield.

412
00:27:33,599 --> 00:27:34,279
Why ended up

413
00:27:34,319 --> 00:27:35,160
like that again?

414
00:27:38,319 --> 00:27:39,000
I thought

415
00:27:39,880 --> 00:27:41,279
I could survive.

416
00:27:44,359 --> 00:27:45,039
Unexpectedly,

417
00:27:46,279 --> 00:27:47,599
I misjudged human nature.

418
00:27:49,440 --> 00:27:51,039
They didn't just silence me

419
00:27:53,799 --> 00:27:54,880
but sought to ensure

420
00:27:56,160 --> 00:27:57,480
I'd never speak again.

421
00:28:00,359 --> 00:28:01,279
Your family

422
00:28:01,720 --> 00:28:02,839
has mastered the art

423
00:28:03,480 --> 00:28:04,799
of deception to perfection.

424
00:28:12,880 --> 00:28:13,440
Master,

425
00:28:14,319 --> 00:28:15,799
news was scarce at Yuhua Temple.

426
00:28:16,359 --> 00:28:16,960
Do you know

427
00:28:17,160 --> 00:28:18,480
how the Xiao family fares now?

428
00:28:18,880 --> 00:28:20,119
Has General Xiao's name

429
00:28:20,319 --> 00:28:21,240
been cleared?

430
00:28:22,720 --> 00:28:23,680
The entire court

431
00:28:23,960 --> 00:28:25,680
condemned Xiao Zhongwu.

432
00:28:26,079 --> 00:28:27,920
To stabilize the court, His Majesty

433
00:28:28,880 --> 00:28:30,119
declared him guilty soon

434
00:28:30,839 --> 00:28:31,559
and almost

435
00:28:31,920 --> 00:28:33,680
took away Xiao Army's
conscription rights.

436
00:28:34,400 --> 00:28:35,400
How could this happen?

437
00:28:35,799 --> 00:28:37,119
Didn't His Majesty investigate?

438
00:28:37,680 --> 00:28:38,640
General Fengyun,

439
00:28:39,279 --> 00:28:40,319
as fellow generals,

440
00:28:40,799 --> 00:28:42,720
I deeply respect General Xiao.

441
00:28:43,599 --> 00:28:45,160
But in matters of righteousness,

442
00:28:45,400 --> 00:28:46,599
we must not speak falsely.

443
00:28:48,279 --> 00:28:49,160
Righteousness?

444
00:28:49,640 --> 00:28:50,759
Does your righteousness

445
00:28:50,759 --> 00:28:51,960
mean delaying reinforcements

446
00:28:52,279 --> 00:28:53,200
and letting my father,

447
00:28:53,680 --> 00:28:55,759
along with 30,000 Xiao soldiers,

448
00:28:56,519 --> 00:28:58,079
die in vain?

449
00:28:59,759 --> 00:29:01,599
I immediately dispatched troops

450
00:29:01,759 --> 00:29:03,359
upon receiving the distress call,

451
00:29:03,440 --> 00:29:04,960
without any delay.

452
00:29:05,599 --> 00:29:07,680
Had I not turned the tide,

453
00:29:08,039 --> 00:29:09,079
Wutuo's cavalry

454
00:29:09,119 --> 00:29:10,519
would have reached here long ago.

455
00:29:13,759 --> 00:29:15,599
As a witness, General Feihong testified

456
00:29:15,960 --> 00:29:16,839
before His Majesty

457
00:29:17,400 --> 00:29:18,279
and firmly insisted

458
00:29:18,359 --> 00:29:19,559
on Xiao Zhongwu's guilt.

459
00:29:20,599 --> 00:29:22,119
With such crucial witnesses present,

460
00:29:22,880 --> 00:29:23,920
they didn't look further.

461
00:29:37,279 --> 00:29:38,599
He Rufei,

462
00:29:39,400 --> 00:29:40,319
it was you

463
00:29:41,039 --> 00:29:42,640
who delayed reinforcement

464
00:29:44,599 --> 00:29:45,799
and caused my father

465
00:29:47,240 --> 00:29:49,160
and the Xiao Army troops

466
00:29:49,480 --> 00:29:50,680
to perish tragically!

467
00:29:52,079 --> 00:29:53,480
Childhood classmates first,

468
00:29:54,359 --> 00:29:55,160
and then

469
00:29:55,440 --> 00:29:57,039
frontier commanders.

470
00:29:59,039 --> 00:30:00,680
He Rufei,

471
00:30:02,599 --> 00:30:04,039
after all these years apart,

472
00:30:06,880 --> 00:30:08,839
