475
00:30:55,920 --> 00:30:56,759
(from now on,)

476
00:30:57,480 --> 00:30:58,720
(I am simply He Yan.)

477
00:31:00,440 --> 00:31:01,559
(In this vast world,)

478
00:31:02,359 --> 00:31:04,000
(I'm no longer anyone's substitute.)

479
00:31:07,240 --> 00:31:09,119
(He Rufei stole my title
as General Feihong,)

480
00:31:09,640 --> 00:31:11,759
(tried to kill me, and ruined my name.)

481
00:31:12,599 --> 00:31:14,200
(I won't let him off.)

482
00:31:18,240 --> 00:31:19,359
(I will return to the army)

483
00:31:20,000 --> 00:31:21,000
